wikipedia_page.main: Nicholas John F. Murphy (22 October 1966 – 1 September 1998) was an English professional footballer who played as a defender in the Football League for York City, and in non-League football for Tadcaster Albion and Magnets.

response: Nicholas or Nick Murphy may also refer to:
*Nick Murphy (director), British film director and television director
*Chet Faker (born Nicholas James Murphy, 1988), Australian musician also known as Nick Murphy
